Package: implicitMeasures
Type: Package
Title: Computes the Scores for Different Implicit Measures
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Ottavia M. Epifania
Maintainer: Ottavia M. Epifania <otta.epifania@gmail.com>
Contributor: Pasquale Anselmi, Egidio Robusto
Description: The scores for the Implicit Association Test (IAT; Greenwald et al., 
    1998) and the Single Category - IAT (SC-IAT; Karpinski & Steinman,
    2006) are computed. For the computation of the IAT D-score, the algorithms in 
    Greenwald et al. (2003) are used. For computing the SC-IAT D, 
    the procedure in Karpinski & Steinman (2006) is 
    used. Several functions for preparing the data (both for the IAT
    and the SC-IAT), plotting the results, and obtaining a table with the
    scores of implicit measures descriptive statistics are provided. 
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
